    "notes": "Magnetic tile (Dataset Ninja Supervisely 배포판). 1344 imgs (free 956 / defect 388, 459 obj), 5 classes (blowhole/break/crack/fray/uneven), all bitmap annotations. prepare_mtd.py normalizes ds/ann(*.jpg.json)+ds/img into MVTec-style layout: train/good, test/{class}/{name}.jpg, ground_truth/{class}/{stem}_mask.png (bitmap base64-zlib-PNG rasterized to full-frame; empty masks skipped). Masks resolved by the mtd _find_mask_path branch (mvtec-style ground_truth/{class}/{stem}_mask.png). Images are .jpg; domain=='mtd' image glob restricted to .jpg/.jpeg. Multi-defect images appear under each present class with a class-union mask."
